5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereceived%20weapons%20from%20Iran%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Politico%20reported%20this%20week%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-sending-russia-masses-of-military-gear-including-drones-report-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20has%20also%20been%20sending%20military%20gear%20to%20Russia%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20drones%20and%20protective%20gear%2C%20relying%20on%20a%20loophole%20to%20get%20around%20Western%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20also%20been%20relying%20on%20weapons%20from%20several%20different%20countries%20in%20the%20war%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-using-anti-aircraft-guns-1940s-shoot-ground-targets-russia-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESoviet-era%20weapons%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fminefields-force-ukraine-to-change-counteroffensive-strategy-russia-2023-7%3Finline-endstory-related-recommendations%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earms%20provided%20by%20the%20West%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Germany%2C%20and%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-using-north-korean-rockets-against-russian-forces-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690590593000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c442d1cf077800196702e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-using-north-korean-rockets-against-russian-forces-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukrainian%20forces%20are%20using%20unreliable%20North%20Korean%20rockets%20against%20Russian%20forces%20despite%20Pyongyang's%20support%20for%20Russia's%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kvlamis%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Vlamis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-using-north-korean-rockets-against-russian-forces-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Agrees%20To%20Hear%20Plea%20On%20Mob%20Violence%20Against%20Muslims%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20agreed%20to%20hear%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%20a%20women's%20organisation%20seeking%20directions%20to%20states%20to%20take%20immediate%20action%20in%20consonance%20with%20a%202018%20verdict%20of%20the%20apex%20court%20to%20effectively%20deal%20with%20incidents%20of%20lynching%20and%20mob%20violence%20against%20Muslims%20by%20cow%20vigilantes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20JB%20Pardiwala%20issued%20notice%20to%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20DGPs%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Orissa%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana%20seeking%20their%20responses%20to%20the%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20National%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Women%20(NFIW)%2C%20an%20organisation%20linked%20to%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%2C%20pleaded%20against%20referring%20the%20matter%20to%20high%20courts%20for%20adjudication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20that%20happens%2C%20then%20I%20will%20have%20to%20go%20to%20various%20high%20courts.%20But%20what%20will%20the%20victims%20get%3F%20Compensation%20of%20two%20lakhs%20after%20ten%20years.%20This%20is%20despite%20the%202018%20verdict%20in%20Tehseen%20Poonawala%20case%20regarding%20mob%20violence.%20What%20remedy%20do%20I%20have%2C%20where%20will%20I%20go%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sibal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20last%20time%20he%20had%20moved%20the%20apex%20court%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20approach%20the%20high%20courts%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20then%20told%20him%20it%20was%20issuing%20notice%20to%20the%20parties%20concerned%20on%20the%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%2C%20filed%20through%20advocate%20Sumita%20Hazarika%20and%20Rashmi%20Singh%2C%20sought%20urgent%20intervention%20of%20the%20apex%20court%20in%20view%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Balarming%26quot%3B%20rise%20in%20cases%20of%20lynching%20and%20mob%20violence%20targeting%20Muslims%20despite%20clear%20guidelines%20and%20directions%20issued%20by%20the%20top%20court%20in%202018%20with%20regard%20to%20cow%20vigilantes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20the%20alarming%20rise%20in%20cases%20of%20lynching%20and%20mob%20violence%20against%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20the%20Petitioner%20is%20seeking%20a%20writ%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20mandamus%20to%20the%20concerned%20State%20authorities%20to%20take%20immediate%20action%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20findings%20and%20directions%20of%20this%20court%20in%20Tehseen%20Poonawalla%20(2018%20verdict)%20so%20as%20to%20effectively%20contain%20and%20deal%20with%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20plea%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20had%20in%202018%20issued%20a%20set%20of%20guidelines%20to%20curb%20cow%20vigilantism%20that%20targeted%20mostly%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20said%20urgent%20relief%20was%20being%20sought%20as%20states%20had%20failed%20to%20take%20necessary%20action%20against%20the%20perpetrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20positive%20duty%20of%20the%20State%20to%20protect%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20and%20freedoms%20of%20all%20individuals%20and%20the%20primary%20responsibility%20of%20the%20State%20to%20foster%20a%20secular%2C%20pluralistic%20and%20multiculturalist%20social%20order%2C%20have%20been%20recognized%20by%20this%20Court%20in%20several%20judgments%20including%20in%20Tehseen%20Poonawalla%20(2018%20verdict).%20It%20is%20further%20submitted%20that%20this%20court%20recognized%20its%20own%20constitutional%20duty%20to%2