ennedy%20Jr.%20on%20Friday%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Biden%20administration%20for%20refusing%20to%20grant%20his%20request%20for%20Secret%20Service%20protection%2C%20a%20complaint%20that%20ignores%20the%20reality%20that%20many%20presidential%20candidates%20are%20not%20granted%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20assassination%20of%20my%20father%20in%201968%2C%20candidates%20for%20president%20are%20provided%20Secret%20Service%20protection.%20But%20not%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Kennedy%20wrote%20on%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy's%20complaint%20comes%20with%20added%20personal%20resonance%20as%20the%20assassination%20of%20his%20father%2C%20New%20York%20Sen.%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%2C%20led%20Congress%20to%20extend%20protection%20to%20major%20party%20presidential%20and%20vice%20presidential%20candidates%20and%20nominees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2008%2F06%2F04%2F91122836%2Frfk-assassination-sparked-secret-service-change%5C%22%3EAs%20NPR%20previously%20recounted%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Secret%20Service%20learned%20almost%20immediately%20that%20it%20could%20not%20protect%20everyone%2C%20even%20though%20they%20tried%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20RFK's%20assassination.%20Agents%20put%20in%20270%2C000%20hours%20of%20overtime%20in%201970%2C%20protecting%20candidates%20and%20other%20prominent%20political%20figures.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20agency%20responded%20by%20implementing%20criteria%20for%20which%20candidates%20are%20eligible%20for%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretservice.gov%2Fprotection%2Fleaders%2Fcampaign-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20entire%20list%20for%202024%20is%20available%20online%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20the%20listed%20criteria%20are%20not%20intended%20to%20be%20exhausted%2C%20they%20include%20steps%20that%20Kennedy%20has%20not%20reached.%20He%20is%20not%20the%20de%20facto%20nominee%20of%20a%20major%20presidential%20party.%20He%20has%20polled%20in%20the%20double%20digits%2C%20but%20he%20has%20not%20averaged%2015%25%20or%20more%20in%20the%20Real%20Clear%20Politics%20Average%20over%20the%20last%2030%20days.%20(He's%20at%2013.7%25).%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20does%20not%20act%20alone%20either.%20Homeland%20Security%20Secretary%20Alejandro%20Mayorkas%20works%20with%20an%20advisory%20committee%20composed%20of%20top%20congressional%20leaders%2C%20such%20as%20Speaker%20Kevin%20McCarthy%20and%20Senate%20Minority%20Leader%20Mitch%20McConnell.%20A%20DHS%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20very%20early%20in%20the%20primary%20calendar%20to%20request%20protection.%20When%20Dr.%20Ben%20Carson%20and%20then-candidate%20Donald%20Trump%20made%20their%20request%20in%202015%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F2016-election%2Fben-carson-donald-trump-request-secret-service-protection-n447266%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20it%20wasn't%20until%20the%20fall%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Their%20requests%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2015%2F11%2F05%2Fpolitics%2Fdonald-trump-ben-carson-secret-service%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Equickly%20signed%20off%20on.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20presidential%20protection%20is%20what%20the%20agency%20is%20known%20for%2C%20the%20Secret%20Service%20is%20also%20responsible%20for%20helping%20provide%20security%20for%20major%20national%20events%20such%20as%20the%20Super%20Bowl.%20Agents%20also%20secure%20foreign%20dignitaries%20during%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly.%C2%A0%20There%20simply%20are%20not%20enough%20agents%20to%20go%20around.%20As%20BuzzFeed%20pointed%20out%20in%202016%2C%20agents%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeednews.com%2Farticle%2Frubycramer%2Fdhs-secretary-promises-secret-service-we-will-fix-unpaid-ove%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehad%20to%20wait%20months%20to%20get%20receive%20their%20overtime%20pay%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20a%20federal%20pay%20cap.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20campaigns%20welcome%20Secret%20Service%20protection%20either.%20Sen.%20John%20McCain's%20campaign%20held%20off%20on%20it%20in%202008.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20while%20a%20protective%20bubble%20from%20world-class%2C%20taxpayer-funded%20agents%20is%20incredible%20it%20also%20makes%20the%20type%20of%20intimate%20campaigning%20the%20early%20primary%20season%20is%20known%20for%20far%20more%20difficult.%20Supporters%20have%20to%20go%20through%20security%20screenings%20and%20often%20are%20asked%20to%20show%20up%20hours%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20fairly%20obvious%20reasons%20why%20Kennedy%20wants%20protection.%20One%20is%20that%20Secret%20Service%20protection%20is%20covered%20by%20taxpayers.%20It's%20not%20immediately%20clear%20how%20much%20money%20his%20campaign%20is%20spending%20on%20security.%20His%20campaign%20did%20not%20specifically%20indicate%20any%20security%20costs%20in%20its%20most%20recent%20FEC%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20Secret%20Service%20agents%20gives%20any%20hopeful%20the%20aura%20of%20being%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20free%20world.%20Kennedy%20has%20lashed%20out%20at%20those%20who%20remind%20him%20of%20his%20past%20statements%20where%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2023%2F07%2F13%2F1187272781%2Frfk-jr-kennedy-conspiracy-theories-social-media-presidential-campaign%5C%22%3Ebear-hugged%20conspiracies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Fvideos%2Fpolitics%2F2023%2F07%2F20%2Frobert-f-kennedy-jr-anti-vax-fact-check-dale-nc-vpx.cnn%5C%22%3Eurged%20parents%20not%20to%20vaccinate%20their%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Frobert-f-kennedy-jr-apologizes-for-holocaust-comment-in-vaccine-debate%2F%5C%22%3Eand%20flirted%20with%20antisemiti