d.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20has%20been%20claiming%20that%20the%20triple%20murder%20case%20in%20Golaghat%20where%20a%2025-year%20old%20Muslim%20man%20killed%20his%20Hindu%20wife%20and%20her%20parents%20on%20Monday%20was%20a%20case%20of%20'love%20jihad'%2C%20a%20term%20used%20by%20right-wing%20groups%20to%20allege%20that%20Muslim%20men%20lure%20Hindu%20women%20to%20convert%20through%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20claimed%20there%20have%20been%20many%20tragic%20incidents%20of%20suicide%20by%20girls%20who%20have%20been%20victims%20of%20'love%20jihad'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%20had%20earlier%20claimed%20on%20Thursday%20that%20there%20will%20be%20peace%20in%20the%20country%20if%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20men%20marry%20women%20of%20their%20respective%20communities.%20The%20chief%20minister%20told%20the%20convention%20that%20another%20operation%20to%20combat%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20state%20will%20be%20launched%20in%20September%20and%20legislative%20backing%20will%20be%20given%20to%20ensure%20prosecution%20of%20the%20accused%20held%20for%20polygamy%20and%20child%20marriages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%20urged%20all%20SPs%20of%20the%20state%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20more%20arrests%20in%20September%20as%20there%20will%20be%20another%20round%20of%20action%20against%20child%20marriage%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Whenever%20a%20child%20marriage%20comes%20to%20our%20notice%20we%20will%20have%20to%20prosecute%20the%20accused%20under%20POCSO%20as%20it%20is%20a%20secular%20Act%20and%20does%20not%20deal%20with%20any%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20POCSO%20Act%20applies%20equally%20to%20all%20citizens%20of%20all%20religions%20who%20commit%20sexual%20offences%20against%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''There%20are%20some%20vintage%20acts%20that%20have%20come%20to%20our%20notice.%20We%20will%20repeal%20them%20as%20it%20comes%20in%20the%20way%20of%20taking%20action%20against%20child%20marriage%2C''%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Sa