%20more%20newfangled%20feature.%20When%20prompted%2C%20I%20hopped%20out%20of%20the%20vehicle%20and%20stared%20straight%20at%20the%20camera%20located%20by%20the%20driver's%20window.%20Within%20just%20a%20second%20or%20two%2C%20the%20GV60%20robotically%20shouted%20%26quot%3Bfacial%20recognition%20set!%26quot%3B%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUsing%20it%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Genesis%20GV60%20electric%20SUV's%20interior.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c3e9f8cf0778001966808a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221702%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Genesis%20GV60.%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDriving%20around%20keyless%20is%20a%20two-step%20process.%20First%2C%20you%20walk%20up%20to%20the%20vehicle%20and%20press%20on%20the%20driver's-side%20door%20handle%20while%20looking%20at%20the%20exterior%20camera.%20That%20unlocks%20the%20GV60.%20The%20first%20few%20times%2C%20I%20stooped%20down%20to%20put%20my%20face%20closer%20to%20the%20car%2C%20but%20then%20I%20realized%20it%20worked%20just%20as%20well%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20better%20%E2%80%94%20to%20just%20stand%20up%20naturally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20in%2C%20you%20touch%20the%20fingerprint%20reader.%20Once%20a%20message%20pops%20up%20saying%20the%20driver%20has%20been%20authenticated%2C%20you%20can%20go%20ahead%20and%20start%20the%20car.%20To%20lock%20up%2C%20you%20repeat%20step%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20my%20surprise%2C%20the%20whole%20system%20worked%20flawlessly%2C%20never%20failing%20to%20recognize%20my%20face%20or%20fingerprint.%20I%20even%20found%20it%20helpful%20sometimes%20%E2%80%94%20for%20example%2C%20when%20I%20wanted%20to%20grab%20something%20from%20the%20car%20on%20my%20way%20out%20the%20door.%20Another%20time%2C%20I%20needed%20to%20reposition%20the%20GV60%20in%20a%20friend's%20driveway%20before%20hopping%20in%20his%20car%20to%20drive%20somewhere.%20Both%20times%2C%20it%20was%20kind%20of%20nice%20to%20not%20carry%20the%20key%20fob%20with%20me%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day%20or%20run%20back%20inside%20to%20ditch%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Genesis%20GV60%20electric%20SUV%2C%20with%20green%20trees%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c3ea77048ff200190cf0c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Genesis%20GV60.%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20had%20used%20the%20feature%20a%20handful%20of%20times%2C%20I%20mustered%20up%20the%20courage%20to%20actually%20go%20for%20a%20drive%20without%20the%20key.%20It's%20a%20weird%20feeling%20to%20drive%20a%20car%20without%20a%20key.%20But%20once%20again%2C%20everything%20went%20off%20without%20a%20hitch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECool%2C%20but%20not%20revolutionary%20%E2%80%94%20yet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biometric%20ID%20system%20performed%20nicely%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20I'd%20use%20it%20all%20that%20often%20if%20I%20actually%20owned%20the%20GV60.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Genesis%20GV60%20electric%20SUV's%20door%20handle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c3e983cf07780019667f88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20someone%20who's%20terrified%20by%20facial%20recognition%20or%20business%20interests%20invading%20my%20privacy.%20In%20fact%2C%20I'm%20actually%20that%20idiot%20who%20just%20clicks%20%26quot%3Baccept%20all%20cookies%26quot%3B%20because%20they're%20too%20lazy%20to%20check%20a%20few%20boxes.%20So%20it's%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20principle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20don't%20think%20it%20makes%20things%20any%20easier.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20it%20actually%20slows%20you%20down.%20With%20the%20regular%20key%2C%20you%20can%20walk%20up%20to%20the%20SUV%2C%20instantly%20unlock%20it%2C%20hop%20in%2C%20and%20drive%20away%2C%20all%20without%20even%20removing%20the%20fob%20from%20your%20pocket.%20It's%20seamless.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Genesis%20GV60%20electric%20SUV's%20steering%20wheel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c3e9f8cf07780019668087%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Genesis%20GV60.%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biometric%20system%20adds%20a%20few%20seconds%20of%20lag%20time%20to%20each%20step%20that%20can%20feel%20unbearably%20long%20when%20your%20brain%20has%20been%20irreversibly%20decayed%20by%20modern%20technology%20and%20the%20instant%20gratification%20it%20provides.%20It%20can%20be%20nice%20to%20lighten%20your%20pockets%20by%20not%20carrying%20a%20key%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20have%20to%20give%20major%20props%20to%20Genesis%20for%20trying%20something%20cool%20and%20new%20%E2%80%94%20but%20at%20least%20for%20now%2C%20the%20key%20provides%20a%20better%20user%20experience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20see%20myself%20leaving%20the%20key%20at%20home%20in%20specific%2C%20rare%20situations%20when%20it's%20best%20to%20carry%20as%20little%20as%20possible%2C%20like%20going%20to%20the%20beach%20or%20on%20a%20bike%20ride.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Genesis%20GV60%20electric%20SUV's%20key%20fob.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c3ea6d048ff200190cf0aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Genesis%20GV60.%3Cp%3ETim%20Levin%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20shou