%20generate%20more%20images%20simultaneously%2C%20produce%20images%20faster%2C%20and%20use%20images%20commercially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20there%20is%20opportunity%20for%20foul%20play%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI%20porn%2C%20as%20users%20can%20create%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-deepfake%3F_gl%3D1*8rmqej*_ga*NDY2MzYxODUxLjE2ODQ3NzE5NDY.*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTY5MDMwMTcwNy4yMjEuMS4xNjkwMzAxNzQwLjI3LjAuMA..%5C%22%3Edeepfake%3C%2Fa%3E%20pornography%20or%20content%20depicting%20minors%20engaging%20in%20sexual%20acts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fatrioc-caught-qtcinderella-ai-picture-twitch-deepfake-controversy-streamer-trauma-2023-2%5C%22%3EAtrioc%2C%20a%20popular%20Twitch%20streamer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20caught%20watching%20this%20pornography%20depicting%20deepfakes%20of%20female%20streamers.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20experts%20told%20Insider%20that%20being%20featured%20in%20non-consensual%20deepfake%20porn%20can%20be%20traumatic%20and%20considered%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChaudhry%20told%20Insider%20in%20February%20that%20Unstable's%20%26quot%3Baggressive%20filter%20and%20moderation%20system%26quot%3B%20prevents%20deepfakes%20and%20other%20undesirable%20content.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20foolproof.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F07%2F21%2Fas-ai-porn-generators-get-better-the-stakes-raise%2F%5C%22%3ETechCrunch%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20able%20to%20use%20the%20generator%20to%20create%20images%20that%20produced%20look-alikes%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Chris%20Hemsworth%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20TechCrunch%20images%2C%20Chaudhry%20said%20that%20the%20look-alikes%20were%20created%20during%20a%20period%20where%20the%20service%20was%20experiencing%20%26quot%3Ba%20bug%20with%20our%20deepfake%20content%20generation%20filter%20that%20temporarily%20disabled%20it%20for%20some%20users.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBug%20or%20not%2C%20perfect%20content%20moderation%2C%20especially%20for%20a%20product%20that%20has%20few%20guard%20rails%20is%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20possible%20because%20of%20Gilb's%20law%20of%20unreliability%20%E2%80%94%20any%20system%20which%20depends%20on%20human%20reliability%20is%20unreliable%2C%26quot%3B%20Dan%20Hendrycks%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-safety-expert-research-speculates-dangers-doomsday-scenarios-weaponization-deception-2023-4%5C%22%3EAI%20safety%20expert%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20director%20of%20the%20Center%20for%20AI%20Safety%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContent%20moderation%20for%20any%20system%20that%20is%20capable%20of%20producing%20inflammatory%20material%20is%20impossible%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20AI%20chatbots%20moderated%20extensively%20by%20tech%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-researchers-jailbreak-bard-chatgpt-safety-rules-2023-7%5C%22%3EGoogle%20and%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20having%20their%20guardrails%20bypassed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20may%20also%20run%20into%20legal%20problems%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Gavin%20Newsom%2C%20the%20Governor%20of%20California%2C%20signed%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-deepfake-laws-politics-porn-free-speech-privacy-experts-2019-10%5C%22%3Edeepfake-related%20bills%20into%20state%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20which%20allowed%20residents%20to%20sue%20anyone%20using%20deepfake%20technology%20that%20inserts%20them%20into%20pornographic%20material%20without%20consent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F118th-congress%2Fhouse-bill%2F3106%2Factions%3Fs%3D1%26r%3D4%5C%22%3Ebill%20was%20introduced%20to%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20would%20make%20it%20illegal%20to%20share%20or%20spread%20non-consensual%2C%20AI-generated%20pornography.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-porn-generator-unstable-making-500k-images-day-ceo-says-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690567562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64bee1a5ed4f460019625aa4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-porn-generator-unstable-making-500k-images-day-ceo-says-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20getting%20booted%20off%20Kickstarter%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%2C%20Unstable%20Diffusion%2C%20a%20NSFW%20image%20generator%2C%20has%20still%20managed%20to%20find%20a%20big%20audience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wgendron%40insider.com%20(Will%20Gendron%2CBeatrice%20Nolan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-porn-generator-unstable-making-500k-images-day-ceo-says-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vietnam%20jails%2050%20in%20mass%20bribery%20trial%20over%20Covid-19%20flights%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690566860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F166DB%2Fproduction%2F_130576819_gettyimages-1559647531.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66340808%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Judges%20said%20the%20accused%20extorted%20money%20from%20people%20taking%20repatriation%20flights%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A144%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66340808%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66340808.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66340808.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sonu%20Nigam%20warns%20people%20against%20a%20scammer%20woman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690566247000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102214825%2Cimgsize-26336.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsonu-nigam-warns-people-against-a-woman-posing-to-be-from-his-social-media-team%2Farticleshow%2F102214893.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102214893.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAs%20soon%20as%20Sonu%20Nigam%20learnt%20about%20the%20social%20media%20scam%2C%20he%20has%20warned%20people%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20this%20person%20in%20question.%20The%20singer%20is%20yet%20to%20file%20a%20police%20complaint%20on%20the%20same.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsonu-nigam-warns-people-against-a-woman-posing-to-be-from-his-social-media-team%2Farticleshow%2F102214893.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Manipur%20Needs%20Healing%2C%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20write%20this%2C%20we%20have%20just%20concluded%20the%20seventh%20day%20of%20parliament.%20No%20sign%20yet%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20inside%20Lok%20Sabha%20or%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20The%20closest%20he%20has%20come%20to%20the%20chambers%20of%20both%20Houses%20is%20to%20address%20the%20media%20somewhere%20in%20the%20precincts%20of%20parliament%20House.%20The%20INDIA%20parties%20(preferred%20usage%20to%20%26quot%3BOpposition%20parties%26quot%3B)%20are%20striving%20to%20get%20a%20discussion%20going%20in%20parliament%20on%20Manipur.%20There%20is%20one%20hitch.%20The%20PM%20does%20not%20want%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20debate.%20The%20INDIA%20parties%20insist%20he%20must.%20Hence%2C%20the%20logjam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20leave%20parliament%20aside%20for%20a%20moment%2C%20and%20consider%20the%20footage%20that%20has%20surfaced%20from%20Manipur.%20Last%20week%20a%20bone-chilling%20video%20was%20circulated%20on%20social%20media.%20Two%20women%20from%20the%20conflict%20ridden%20state%20were%20being%20paraded%20naked%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20men%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20seemed%20to%20be%20teenagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20several%20details%20have%20emerged.%20What%20we%20know%20so%20far%20is%20that%20this%20incident%20occured%20soon%20after%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20erupted.%20That%20it%20was%20caused%20in%20retaliation%20to%20a%20piece%20of%20fake%20news%20that%20went%20viral%20in%20early%20May.%20This%20piece%20of%20false%20news%20showed%20the%20image%20of%20a%20young%20woman%20wrapped%20in%20a%20plastic%20bag.%20The%20claim%20was%20that%20she%20was%20from%20a%20particular%20ethnic%20group%2C%20and%20had%20been%20raped%20and%20killed%20by%20men%20from%20a%20rival%20group.%20As%20it%20was%20discovered%20later%2C%20the%20woman%20was%20a%20Delhi%20murder%20victim%20from%202022.%20The%20image%20enraged%20men%20belonging%20to%20one%20group%2C%20who%20then%20abducted%20the%20women%20who%20appeared%20in%20the%20video%20and%20revenge%20raped%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20gets%20worse.%20Even%20though%20an%20FIR%20was%20filed%20days%20later%20in%20May%2C%20it%20is%20only%20after%20the%20video%20generated%20social%20media%20traction%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%2C%20and%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20commented%20on%20it.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20hundreds%20of%20similar%20FIRs%20here%26quot%3B.%20Extending%20the%20apathy%20and%20inefficiency%2C%20'South%20Asia's%20Leading%20Multimedia%20News%20Agency'%20(guess%20who!)%20put%20out%20yet%20another%20piece%20of%20fake%20news%2C%20incorrectly%20implicating%20a%20man%20from%20a%20minority%20community%20as%20one%20of%20those%20arrested%20in%20the%20case.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20any%20piece%20of%20information%20has%20the%20power%20to%20do%20irreversible%20damage%20to%20both%20communities%2C%20how%20can%20a%20government's%20actions%20be%20guided%20only%20by%20what's%20trending%20on%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20root%20of%20the%20gruesome%20assault%20are%20two%20issues.%20One%2C%20the%20government%20failed%20to%20control%20the%20spread%20of%20false%20information%20that%20caused%20the%20rape%20and%20shameful%20parading%20of%20the%20women.%20In%20this%20light%2C%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau's%20(PIB)%20recent%20admission%20that%20it%20only%20acted%20upon%201%2C200%20of%20the%201.2%20lakh%20fake%20news%20requests%20it%20received%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%20seems%20less%20shocking.%20Two%2C%20despite%20knowing%20well%20in%20advance%2C%20the%20union%20government%20failed%20to%20stop%20an%20uncensored%20version%20of%20the%20video%20from%20being%20circulated%20on%20social%20media.%20In%20response%20to%20a%20question%20by%20this%20columnist%20in%20parliament%2C%20the%20government%20admitted%20blocking%20635%20URLs%20on%20the%20internet%20since%20December%202021.%20Where%20was%20this%20promptness%20when%20the%20dignity%20of%20Manipur's%20women%20was%20under%20threat%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20case%20of%20sexual%20assault%20surfaces%20when%20parliament%20is%20in%20session.%20Multiple%20parties%20are%20demanding%20a%20discussion%20under%20the%20'emergency%20rules'%20of%20parliament%2C%20given%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20other%20ideas.%20But%20if%20everything%20was%20so%20hunky%20dory%20in%20Manipur%2C%20then%20why%20has%20the%20internet%20been%20shut%20down%20for%20nearly%20three%20months%3F%20Was%20the%20internet%20shut%20down%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20other%20states%20that%20the%20BJP%20draws%20parallels%20with%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20that%20reached%20the%20internet%20is%20one%20that%20we%20know%20of.%20If%20previous%20cycles%20of%20fake%20news%20distribution%20are%20to%20be%20relied%20on%20as%20evidence%2C%20that%20single%20fake%20image%20might%20have%20already%20caused%20several%20other%20acts%20of%20violence.%20These%20may%20never%20reach%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20mug%20shots%20are%20splattered%20all%20over%20the%20country%20on%20G20%20hoardings%2C%20with%20the%20tagline%20'One%20Earth.%20One%20Family.%20One%20Future'.%20But%20before%20that%2C%20Manipur%20needs%20healing.%20Today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FdyxoRB2w2YQ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Opinion%3A%20Manipur%20Needs%20Healing%2C%20Today%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20research%3A%20Varnika%20Mishra%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690566180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F7q2a0i9o_manipur-violence-ani_625x300_30_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmanipur-needs-healing-today-4249858%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Prime%20Minister's%20mug%20shots%20are%20splattered%20all%20over%20the%20country%20on%20G20%20hoardings%2C%20with%20the%20tagline%20'One%20Earth.%20One%20Family.%20One%20Future'.%20But%20before%20that%2C%20Manipur%20needs%20healing.%20Today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmanipur-needs-healing-today-4249858%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmanipur-needs-heal