%20(FTA)%20this%20year%20as%20both%20countries%20have%20reached%20consensus%20on%20the%20broad%20contours%20of%20the%20proposed%20deal%20aiming%20to%20boost%20economic%20growth%20and%20jobs%2C%20a%20top%20trade%20ministry%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20finalise%20the%20deal%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunil%20Barthwal%2C%20India's%20commerce%20secretary%2C%20told%20reporters%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20on%20almost%20all%20contentious%20issues%2C%20negotiations%20were%20completed%2C%20and%20the%20deal%20could%20be%20signed%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20before%26quot%3B%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20sees%20an%20FTA%20with%20Britain%20as%20crucial%20to%20hopes%20of%20becoming%20a%20bigger%20exporter%2C%20while%20the%20UK%20would%20obtain%20wider%20access%20for%20its%20whisky%2C%20premium%20cars%20and%20legal%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20India%2C%20an%20FTA%20with%20the%20UK%20would%20be%20its%20first%20with%20a%20developed%20country%20after%20it%20signed%20an%20interim%20trade%20pact%20with%20Australia%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Britain%2C%20it%20is%20part%20of%20a%20quest%20for%20diversified%20global%20trade%20relationships%20after%20its%202020%20exit%20from%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20at%20a%20crucial%20time%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20wants%20to%20solidify%20India's%20business-friendly%20image%20ahead%20of%20national%20elections%20early%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2011th%20round%20of%20talks%20was%20concluded%20recently%20in%20London%20during%20a%20visit%20by%20Barthwal%20and%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20total%2026%20chapters%20in%20the%20FTA%2C%20discussions%20on%2019%20have%20been%20closed%20including%20issues%20related%20to%20the%20sensitive%20automobile%20sector%2C%20Mr%20Barthwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20countries%20have%20yet%20to%20iron%20out%20differences%20on%20intellectual%20property%20rights%2C%20rules%20of%20origin%20and%20an%20investment%20treaty%2C%20separate%20trade%20ministry%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20agreement%20in%20principle%20has%20been%20reached%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20rules%20of%20investment%20but%20modalities%20are%20still%20being%20worked%20out%20by%20customs%20authorities%20of%20both%20countries%2C%20r%20Barthwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20is%20final%20till%20everything%20is%20final%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20details%20of%20concessions%20India%20was%20offering%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20next%20round%20of%20negotiations%20will%20be%20held%20shortly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20pushing%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bzero%20tariff%26quot%3B%20for%20textile%2C%20leather%20and%20other%20labour-intensive%20manufacturing%20sectors%20while%20Britain%20had%20sought%20tariff%20concessions%20in%20other%20areas%2C%20said%20Barthwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilateral%20trade%20between%20India%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20rose%2016.6%25%20year-on-year%20to%20%2420.42%20billion%20in%20the%202022%2F23%20fiscal%20year%20ending%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690557720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fjheghqr4_narendra-modi-rishi-sunak-ani_625x300_16_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-could-sign-trade-deal-with-uk-this-year-top-official-4249470%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20and%20Britain%20could%20sign%20a%20free%20trade%20agreement%20(FTA)%20this%20year%20as%20both%20countries%20have%20reached%20consensus%20on%20the%20broad%20contours%20of%20the%20proposed%20deal%20aiming%20to%20boost%20economic%20grow