It%20has%20not%20been%20decided%20where%20the%20meeting%20will%20take%20place.%20The%20meeting%20will%20likely%20be%20attended%20by%20all%20those%20(state%20body%20officials)%20who%20support%20him%20(Brij%20Bhushan)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Tomar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20presidents%20and%20secretaries%20of%20the%20various%20state%20associations%20will%20likely%20come%20for%20the%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20the%20candidates%20for%20the%20elections.%20The%20venue%20for%20the%20meeting%20has%20not%20been%20decided%20as%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Tomar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20date%20for%20filing%20nominations%20for%20the%20August%2012%20elections%20is%20July%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrij%20Bhushan%20is%20not%20eligible%20to%20contest%20as%20he%20has%20already%20completed%2012%20years%20as%20an%20office-bearer%2C%20which%20is%20the%20maximum%20term%20allowed%20as%20per%20the%20National%20Sports%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day-to-day%20affairs%20of%20the%20WFI%20are%20currently%20being%20managed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association-constituted%20ad-hoc%20committee%20led%20by%20Bhupender%20Singh%20Bajwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20Wrestling%20Association%20secretary%20Ranbir%20Kundu%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20so%20far%20his%20state%20association%20had%20not%20received%20invite%20from%20any%20quarter%20or%20candidate%20to%20attend%20their%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20far%2C%20we%20have%20not%20received%20any%20invite.%20We%20are%20not%20going%20to%20field%20any%20candidate%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20for%20the%20top%20posts.%20However%2C%20we%20will%20vote%20for%20truth%20and%20the%20betterment%20of%20wrestling%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kundu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20Punjab%20Wrestling%20Association's%20president%2C%20renowned%20former%20grappler%20Kartar%20Singh%2C%20was%20a%20secretary-general%20of%20the%20WFI%20until%20he%20was%20removed%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20representatives%20from%20each%20state%20unit%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20and%20Tripura%20will%20not%20have%20any%20representatives%20at%20the%20elections%20as%20the%20Returning%20Officer%20deemed%20claims%20of%20both%20factions%20from%20the%20former%20%26quot%3Bineligible%26quot%3B%20while%20Tripura%20has%20remained%20disaffiliated%20since%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WFI%20elections%20are%20taking%20place%20after%20several%20postponements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOA)%20ad-hoc%20panel%20had%20initially%20scheduled%20the%20elections%20for%20July%206%20but%20it%20was%20forced%20to%20reschedule%20the%20polls%20to%20July%2011%20after%20disaffiliated%20state%20bodies%20from%20Maharashtra%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20approached%20it%20for%20a%20hearing%2C%20claiming%20that%20their%20dismissal%20was%20not%20appropriate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IOA%20panel%20heard%20the%20aggrieved%20representatives%20of%20the%20state%20bodies%20but%20the%20polls%20could%20not%20go%20ahead%20even%20on%20July%2011%20with%20the%20Gauhati%20High%20Court%20staying%20the%20elections%20after%20the%20Assam%20Wrestling%20Association%20(AWA)%20sought%20the%20right%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20poll%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20then%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20elections%20after%20staying%20the%20Gauhati%20High%20Court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20nominations%20will%20be%20conducted%20on%20August%202%20and%20a%20final%20list%20of%20the%20candidates%20will%20be%20published%20on%20August%207.%20If%20an%20election%20is%20required%2C%20voting%20will%20be%20conducted%20on%20August%2012.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A169