22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F15190825%2Fimage-652-1024x446.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F15190825%2Fimage-652-300x131.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F15190825%2Fimage-652.png%201138w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-632885%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22366%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EByju%E2%80%99s%20CEO%20Byju%20Raveendran.%20Photo%3A%20cherian_in%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-2.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20FY2016-17%2C%20about%20one%20Indian%20unicorn%20was%20being%20founded%20every%20year.%20Over%20the%20past%20four%20years%20(since%20FY2017-18)%2C%20this%20number%20has%20been%20increasing%20exponentially.%20As%20of%20May%2031%2C%202023%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcfo.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fleadership%2F67-cfos-in-indian-unicorns-dont-have-prior-startup-experience-study%2F101135512%5C%22%3Ewas%20home%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20108%20unicorns%20with%20a%20total%20valuation%20of%20%24340.80%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20these%2C%2044%20with%20a%20total%20valuation%20of%20%2493%20billion%20were%20born%20in%202021%20and%2021%20with%20a%20total%20valuation%20of%20%2427.00%20billion%20in%202022.%20According%20to%20market%20research%20platform%20Tracxn%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Fentrepreneurship%2Fstory%2Fonly-17-out-of-80-unicorns-in-india-are-profitable-6-start-ups-listed-so-far-373233-2023-03-13%5C%22%3Ehas%20only%2017%20profitable%20unicorns.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EByju%E2%80%99s%2C%20Oyo%2C%20Udaan%2C%20Eruditus%2C%20Unacademy%2C%20Swiggy%2C%20and%20PhonePe%20are%20among%20the%20most%20celebrated%20unicorns.%20What%20is%20common%20to%20most%20of%20them%3F%20They%20have%20all%20run%20up%20huge%20losses%20of%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%204%2C500%20crore%20and%20are%20now%20discovering%20that%20incessant%20venture%20funding%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20sustainable%20proposition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20two%20ways%20of%20looking%20at%20unicorns.%20For%20some%2C%20they%20are%20a%20sign%20of%20increased%20technological%20prowess%20achieved%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20For%20others%2C%20unicorns%20are%20artificial%20creations%2C%20financial%20bubbles%20waiting%20to%20burst.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20truth%20lies%20somewhere%20in%20between.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20valuation%20of%20unicorns%20is%20quite%20subjective%20because%20they%20are%20in%20the%20earliest%20stage%20of%20their%20growth.%20They%20do%20not%20have%20financial%20records%20or%20performance%20records%20which%20could%20support%20a%20billion-dollar%20valuation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20good%20number%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20would%20have%20been%20a%20negative%20cash%20flow.%20Unicorns%20are%20based%20on%20perceptions%2C%20rather%20than%20knowledge.%20Perception%20is%20based%20on%20the%20assumption%20that%20these%20firms%20have%20a%20strong%20value%20proposition%20that%20their%20competitors%20can%E2%80%99t%20imitate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInvestors%20and%20founders%20have%20collaborated%20smartly%20to%20create%20hype%20about%20these%20startups%2C%20increase%20their%20valuation%2C%20drive%20up%20their%20brand%20value%2C%20list%20them%20on%20the%20bourses%20at%20high%20%2Cand%20exit%20with%20handsome%20profits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnsuspecting%20market%20investors%20who%20bought%20in%20have%20lost%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20This%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20surprising%2C%20since%20the%20valuation%20of%20unicorns%20is%20beyond%20the%20comprehension%20of%20average%20investors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMere%20market%20share%20gains%20through%20mindless%20acquisitions%20and%20brash%20spends%20on%20branding%20for%20bolstering%20mindshare%20will%20not%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20avers%20R.%20Ramkumar%2C%20former%20CMD%20of%20Cognizant%20India%2C%20who%20is%20now%20pro%20vice-chancellor%20for%20professional%20learning%20at%20Krea%20University.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Findia-is-generating-many-unicorns-and-decacorns-but-who-gains-from-them%5C%22%3EIndia%20Is%20Generating%20Many%20Unicorns%20and%20Decacorns%2C%20But%20Who%20Gains%20From%20Them%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnicorns%20are%20encountering%20new%20challenges%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fstartup-funding-india-drop-33-percent-2022%5C%22%3Efunding%20winters%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fforeign-investments-into-indian-startup-ecosystem-fall-by-72-in-2023-so-far-report%5C%22%3Evaluation%20markdowns%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Oyo%2C%20Swiggy%2C%20Byju%E2%80%99s%2C%20Meesho%2C%20Eruditus%2C%20PineLabs%2C%20PharmEasy%20and%20the%20like%20are%20hit%20by%20valuation%20markdowns%20%E2%80%93%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20up%20to%2070%25.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20have%20implications%20for%20future%20funding%20rounds%20and%20also%20for%20their%20listing%20plans%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramkumar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fast-evolving%20trend%20has%20triggered%20panic%20and%20extreme%20cost-cutting.%20The%20disproportionately%20high%20visibility%20of%20unicorns%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20double-edged%20weapon%2C%20as%20their%20precipitous%20fall%20is%20also%20getting%20substantial%20scrutiny.%20They%20have%20to%20now%20demonstrate%20a%20path%20to%20sustained%20revenue%20and%20profit%20growth%2C%20via%20pink%20slips%20and%20cost-cutting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerception-led%20valuations%20based%20on%20speculative%20market%20tides%20did%20trigger%20a%20kind%20of%20bull%20run%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20over.%20We%20have%20earlier%20seen%20the%20slide%20of%20dotcoms%20and%20e-commerce.%20This%20time%2C%20it%20was%20e-enabled%20services.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUnreal%2C%20overpriced%20and%20unsustainable%20valuations%20let%20promoters%20and%20interim%20investors%20indulge%20in%20shortcuts%20and%20unethical%20practices%20to%20sustain%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20S.%20Narendran%2C%20a%20former%20executive%20of%20TVS%20Electronics%20and%20a%20data%20scientist.%20%E2%80%9CEntrepreneurs%20are%20lovable%20mavericks%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramkumar%2C%20and%20they%20become%20the%20fall%20guys.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20about%20the%20boards%20of%20these%20firms%2C%20whose%20members%20guide%20the%20strategic%20investment%2C%20growth%20and%20profitability%20agenda%20of%20start-ups%3F%20%E2%80%9CLike%20coaches%20of%20sporting%20teams%2C%20they%20need%20to%20advise%20on%20building%20all%20the%20muscles%20for%20unicorns%20to%20grow%20gracefully%20and%20become%20proficorns%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramkumar%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20proficorn%20is%20a%20rarity%20%E2%80%95%20a%20privately%20held%20start-up%20company%20that%20is%20profitable.%20It%20requires%20not%20hype%2C%20but%20strategic%20thinking%20and%20managing%20talent%2C%20leadership%2C%20risk%20and%20stakeholder%20interest.%20Many%20entrepreneurs%20look%20up%20to%20coaching%20support%2C%20so%20boards%20are%20also%20responsible%20for%20the%20misdirected%20focus%20of%20unicorns.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpoor-working-conditions-abusive-practices-byjus-staff-reveal-harsh-work-conditions%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Treated%20Like%20Slaves%2C%20Abusive%20Practices%E2%80%99%3A%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20Staff%20Reveal%20Harsh%20Work%20Conditions%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInternet%20Slide%203.0%20holds%20lessons%20for%20entrepreneurs%20and%20investors.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cocktail%20of%20greedy%20people%20and%20easy%20money%20seems%20to%20have%20left%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20with%20really%20bad%20hangovers%2C%E2%80%9D%20quips%20the%20former%20head%20of%20a%20leading%20non-bank%20financial%20company%20(NBFC).%20That%20sector%20was%20done%20in%20by%20the%20shenanigans%20of%20unincorporated%20finance%20companies%2C%20which%20used%20advertising%20to%20create%20hype%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20NBFCs%20are%20tightly%20regulated.%20The%20troubles%20of%20unicorns%20like%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20suggest%20that%20it%20is%20imprudent%20to%20build%20a%20business%20which%20depends%20on%20incessant%20venture%20funding.%20When%20money%20is%20easy%2C%20these%20startups%20will%20have%20a%20good%20ride%2C%20but%20when%20the%20money%20flow%20dwindles%20%E2%80%93%20as%20it%20is%20happening%20now%20%E2%80%93%20reality%20catches%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnirudh%20Ravi%20Narayanan%2C%20CEO%20and%20co-founder%20of%20electric%20motorcycle%20maker%20Bharat%20New-Energy%20Company%20(formerly%20Boom%20Motors)%2C%20suggests%20that%20companies%20must%20have%20a%20clear%20product-market%20fit%20and%20clear%20unit%20economics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20funding%20has%20dried%20up%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20surprised%20if%20more%20unicorns%20and%20soonicorns%20(soon-to-be%20unicorns)%20exit%20the%20scene%20or%20valuations%20come%20crashing%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECan%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20and%20the%20like%20be%20brushed%20aside%20as%20isolated%20instances%20of%20over-stretch%3F%20They%20show%20that%20hype%20has%20a%20limited%20shelf-life.%20The%20valuation%20game%20just%20isn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20to%20foster%20a%20sustainable%20business%20and%20ensure%20long-haul%20survival.%20It%20is%20time%20that%20unicorns%20woke%20up%20to%20the%20realities%20of%20business%20dynamics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewir