0target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20curb%20rumours%20and%20disinformation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20quell%20violent%20ethnic%20clashes%20that%20have%20killed%20at%20least%20125%20people%20and%20displaced%20tens%20of%20thousands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20internet%20ban%20in%20the%20state%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eamong%20the%20longest%20in%20India%20to%20date%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20alert%20authorities%20and%20journalists%20to%20rights%20violations%2C%20many%20of%20them%20directed%20at%20women%2C%20activists%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20was%20no%20internet%20shutdown%2C%20those%20videos%20would%20have%20surfaced%20over%20two%20months%20ago%20and%20the%20horror%20could%20have%20been%20addressed%20speedily%2C%20and%20other%20similar%20offences%20could%20have%20been%20curbed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Patricia%20Mukhim%2C%20an%20activist%20and%20editor%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EShillong%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20daily%20headquartered%20in%20Meghalaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-police-women-video-paraded-naked%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Manipur%20Police%20Were%20Present%2C%20But%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Help%20Us%E2%80%99%3A%20Women%20in%20Harrowing%20Video%20Tell%20%E2%80%98The%20Wire%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20internet%20shutdown%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20human%20rights%20%E2%80%93%20it%20curtails%20people%E2%80%99s%20freedom%2C%20and%20it%20shuts%20out%20news%20of%20violent%20incidents%20and%20allows%20perpetrators%20to%20carry%20on%20undeterred%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EContext%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shutdowns%20also%20have%20an%20%E2%80%9Cadverse%20impact%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20feel%20safe%20and%20restrict%20their%20freedom%20of%20movement%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jayshree%20Bajoria%2C%20an%20associate%20director%20at%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20a%20horrific%20video%20of%20violence%20against%20women%20in%20Manipur%20to%20emerge%20on%20social%20media%20for%20the%20authorities%20to%20take%20action.%20This%20shows%20how%20necessary%20the%20internet%20is%20for%20the%20flow%20of%20information%2C%20and%20reporting%20and%20documenting%20abuses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20restore%20the%20internet%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Climited%20fashion%E2%80%9D%2C%20authorities%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20they%20had%20%E2%80%9Cconditionally%E2%80%9D%20lifted%20the%20ban%20on%20broadband%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20websites%2C%20WiFi%20hotspots%2C%20virtual%20private%20networks%20(VPNs)%20and%20mobile%20internet%20%E2%80%93%20used%20by%20a%20majority%20of%20people%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdigitaldutta%2Fstatus%2F1683814915189145601%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estill%20remain%20blocked%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdverse%20impact%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.accessnow.org%2Finternet-shutdowns-2022%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20number%20of%20shutdowns%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20the%20fifth%20successive%20year%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20Access%20Now%2C%20a%20digital%20rights%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shutdowns%20%E2%80%93%20including%20during%20protests%2C%20elections%20and%20examinations%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ewere%20often%20imposed%20for%20indefinite%20periods%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.accessnow.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F2022-KIO-Report-final.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithout%20the%20publication%20of%20shutdown%20orders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20a%202020%20judgment%20by%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAuthorities%20have%20cited%20violence%20as%20part%20of%20the%20rationale%20for%20shutting%20down%20the%20internet.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20to%20show%20internet%20shutdowns%20reduce%20violence%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3Equite%20the%20opposite%2C%E2%80%9D%20Access%20Now%20said%20in%20a%20report%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20Behind%20the%20Manipur%20Violence%20and%20Why%20Stopping%20It%20Poses%20a%20Test%20For%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20borders%20Myanmar%2C%20began%20when%20members%20of%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Naga%20tribal%20groups%20launched%20a%20protest%20on%20May%203%20against%20the%20possible%20sharing%20of%20their%20benefits%20with%20the%20ethnic%20majority%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20government%20rushed%20thousands%20of%20paramilitary%20and%20army%20troops%20to%20the%20state%20of%203.2%20million%20people%2C%20but%20the%20state%20has%20remained%20tense%20since%2C%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Fwhy-is-indias-manipur-state-grip-ethnic-violence-2023-07-21%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekillings%20and%20other%20incidents%20of%20sporadic%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restive%20northeast%20region%20is%20among%20the%20least%20developed%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20patchy%20internet%20access%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finternetshutdowns.in%2F%5C%22%3Efacing%20frequent%20shutdowns%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20data%20compiled%20by%20the%20Software%20Freedom%20Law%20Center%2C%20a%20digital%20rights%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20services%20are%20digitised%20under%20the%20Digital%20India%20programme%2C%20internet%20shutdowns%20disproportionately%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hrw.org%2Freport%2F2023%2F06%2F14%2Fno-internet-means-no-work-no-pay-no-food%2Finternet-shutdowns-deny-access-basic%3Fref%3Dstatic.internetfreedom.in%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehurt%20rural%20communities%20and%20other%20vulnerable%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20those%20who%20depend%20on%20social%20welfare%20benefits%2C%20a%20recent%20report%20by%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20and%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%20(IFF)%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EToll%20on%20women%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20shutdowns%2C%20Indian%20authorities%20also%20frequently%20block%20websites%20and%20issue%20takedown%20orders%20to%20social%20media%20platforms.%20The%20government%20issued%20nearly%207%2C000%20takedown%20orders%20of%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20accounts%20last%20year%20compared%20to%206%2C000%20in%202021%2C%20according%20to%20Access%20Now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20shutdowns%20involve%20blocking%20the%20internet%20on%20mobile%20phones%2C%20which%20is%20how%20most%20of%20the%20population%2C%20particularly%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20access%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20severely%20impacts%20access%20to%20education%20and%20livelihoods%2C%20particularly%20for%20rural%20women%2C%20the%20report%20by%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20and%20IFF%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20has%20had%20the%20most%20internet%20shutdowns%20after%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20workers%20in%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20rural%20employment%20guarantee%20programme%20are%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20attendance%20checks%20and%20wage%20payments%20for%20workers%20have%20been%20digitised%2C%20frequent%20internet%20shutdowns%20in%20the%20state%20mean%20that%20many%20women%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20to%20work%2C%20or%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20paid%2C%20said%20Bajoria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20women%20come%20from%20socially%20and%20economically%20marginalised%20households%20%E2%80%A6%20shutdowns%20that%20cut%20off%20internet%20access%20make%20their%20situation%20worse%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Manipur%2C%20the%20shutdown%20means%20that%20women%20cannot%20communicate%20as%20easily%20with%20their%20families%20via%20WhatsApp%2C%20check%20the%20news%2C%20make%20and%20receive%20payments%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20or%20even%20recharge%20their%20mobile%20SIMs%2C%20said%20Ninglun%20Hangal%2C%20who%20works%20with%20development%20non-profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnable%20to%20work%20from%20home%20because%20of%20the%20internet%20ban%2C%20Hangal%20travelled%2013%20hours%20to%20relocate%20to%20neighbouring%20Assam%20state.%20But%20for%20women%20forced%20to%20stay%20back%2C%20conditions%20are%20tough%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20more%20rumours%20and%20misinformation%20circulating%2C%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20way%20to%20check%20or%20clarify%20what%20is%20true%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWomen%20feel%20isolated%20and%20scared%20for%20their%20safety%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20taking%20a%20terrible%20toll.%20More%20cases%20of%20assault%20and%20abuse%20are%20bound%20to%20come%20to%20light%20when%20the%20internet%20is%20restored.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.context.news%2Fdigital-rights%2Findia-internet-shutdowns-hurt-women-more-manipur-assaults-show%3Futm_source%3Dcopy-url%26utm_medium%3Dshare%26utm_campaign%3Dcontext-share%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.context.news%2Fdigital-rights%2Findia-healt