be.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DepYiGd853mQ%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECholi%20Ke%20Peechhe%20Kya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DepYiGd853mQ%5C%22%3E%20Hai%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKhal%20Nayak%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(1993).%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20glorious%20scene%20where%20Johar%20not%20just%20tells%20us%20about%20his%20disdain%20for%20such%20business-deal%20like%20arranged%20marriage%20meetings%2C%20but%20also%20does%20so%20while%20being%20steeped%20in%20his%20love%20for%20(tacky)%20Hindi%20film%20music.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FWqgXEZkgHrc%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20touted%20as%20the%20blue-eyed%20boy%20of%20the%20young%2C%20mainstream%20Bollywood%20about%2025%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20took%20only%20a%20few%20years%20for%20Johar%E2%80%99s%20limitations%20as%20a%20filmmaker%20to%20start%20showing.%20With%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20Ashutosh%20Gowarikers%20and%20Farhan%20Akhtars%20around%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20millennium%2C%20Johar%E2%80%99s%20ostentatious%20productions%20began%20to%20look%20vacuous.%20It%20resulted%20in%20Johar%20meddling%20with%20his%20natural%20style%20%E2%80%93%20trying%20to%20make%20something%20topical%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20Name%20Is%20Khan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%202009)%2C%20trying%20to%20appease%20a%20younger%20audience%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EStudent%20of%20the%20Year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%202012)%2C%20making%20a%20relatively%20more%20rooted%20and%20raw%20film%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAe%20Dil%20Hai%20Mushkil%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%202016).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20been%20nearly%20two%20decades%20since%20Johar%20sacrificed%20scale%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20good%20to%20see%20him%20return%20to%20what%20might%20be%20considered%20his%20forte.%20The%20frames%20(by%20cinematographer%20Manush%20Anand)%20are%20wider%2C%20each%20and%20every%20character%20seems%20air-brushed%2C%20the%20lead%20actors%20are%20given%20%E2%80%98professions%E2%80%99%20that%20look%20laughably%20plastic%2C%20regional%20stereotypes%20are%20dialled%20to%20the%20volume%20of%2011%2C%20the%20production%20design%20seems%20to%20have%20the%20budget%20of%20a%20small%20country%E2%80%99s%20GDP.%20It%E2%80%99s%20deliberately%20light-weight%2C%20blindingly%20glossy%2C%20unhealthily%20sweet%20and%20yet%20witty%20when%20you%20least%20expect%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERocky%20Randhawa%20(Ranveer%20Singh)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20scion%20of%20the%20Randhawa%20family%E2%80%99s%20Dhanlaxmi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eladdoo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20empire%2C%20named%20after%20and%20built%20by%20his%20grandmother%20(Jaya%20Bachchan)%20%E2%80%93%20opens%20the%20film%20with%20a%20charm-offensive%20voiceover%2C%20introducing%20his%20family%20members.%20Bachchan%2C%20who%20has%20spent%20a%20lifetime%20playing%20stoic%2C%20meek%20characters%2C%20is%20refreshingly%20cast%20as%20the%20acidic%20matriarch%20of%20the%20Randhawa%20household.%20Motivated%20by%20her%20quest%20for%20wealth%2C%20and%20disappointed%20by%20her%20husband%20Kanwal%E2%80%99s%20(Dharmendra)%20artistic%20pursuits%2C%20she%20names%20her%20son%2C%20Tijori%20(Aamir%20Bashir)%20and%20rules%20%E2%80%98Randhawa%20paradise%E2%80%99%20(hilariously%20modelled%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20White%20House)%20with%20an%20iron%20fist.%20One%20day%20Kanwal%2C%20who%20after%20an%20accident%20which%20makes%20him%20wheelchair-bound%20and%20suffering%20irregular%20bouts%20of%20amnesia%2C%20starts%20uttering%20a%20name%20%E2%80%98Jamini%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERocky%20looks%20into%20it.%20Sure%20enough%2C%20one%20Google%20search%20later%2C%20he%20finds%20out%20that%20the%20woman%20he%E2%80%99s%20referring%20to%20is%20related%20to%20a%20primetime%20news%20anchor%2C%20Rani%20Chatterjee%20(Alia%20Bhatt).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20two%20comets%20colliding%20into%20one%20another%2C%20Rocky%20and%20Rani%20meet%2C%20but%20initially%20to%20help%20complete%20the%20love%20story%20of%20Kanwal%20and%20Jamini%20(Shabana%20Azmi)%2C%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20grandmother.%20Seeing%20Rocky%E2%80%99s%20perfectly-chiselled%20torso%20behind%20his%20barely-buttoned%20shirt%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20lust%20at%20first%20sight%20for%20Rani.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160317%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-3.58.25.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160317%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-3.58.25.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160317%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-3.58.25-300x127.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160317%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-3.58.25-1024x434.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22509%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Rocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20inspired%20montage%20of%20recreated%20old%20Hindi%20film%20songs%2C%20Johar%20shows%20Kanwal%20and%20Jamini%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20popular%20lovers%E2%80%99%20spots%2C%20only%20to%20show%20another%20love%20story%20blooming%20in%20the%20background.%20As%20the%20elderly%20couple%20sits%20on%20a%20bench%2C%20the%20younger%20couple%20dance%20at%20a%20distance%2C%20almost%20like%20their%20alter-egos.%20Johar%20is%20able%20to%20paint%20the%20love%20stories%20of%20two%20generations%20%E2%80%93%20one%20that%20finds%20solitude%20in%20their%20late%20years%2C%20while%20passions%20rage%20and%20bodies%20intertwine%20without%20much%20thought%20or%20deliberation%20in%20the%20other.%20Dharmendra%20and%20Shabana%20Azmi%20are%20an%20inspired%20choice%20for%20a%20couple%2C%20given%20their%20%E2%80%98schools%E2%80%99%20of%20acting.%20There%E2%80%99s%20something%20sincere%20about%20them%20as%20frail%2C%20longing%20elders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERocky%20and%20Rani%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20title%20of%20the%20film%20suggests%20%E2%80%93%20are%20destined%20to%20fall%20in%20love.%20However%2C%20not%20before%20a%20social%20experiment%20that%20includes%20them%20living%20with%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20families%20for%20three%20months%2C%20so%20as%20to%20overcome%20the%20significant%20gap%20in%20their%20cultural%20upbringing.%20Johar%2C%20never%20shying%20away%20from%20a%20joke%20to%20mine%20the%20cultural%20differences%2C%20makes%20a%20joke%20about%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20being%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%98Dadaji%E2%80%99%20by%20Rocky.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20another%20scene%20Tota%20Roy%20Chowdhury%20%E2%80%93%20playing%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20father%20Chandan%2C%20a%20Kathak%20dancer%20by%20vocation%20%E2%80%94%20is%20shown%20to%20be%20doing%20hand%20movements%20while%20being%20seated%20in%20Rocky%E2%80%99s%20living%20room%2C%20stressing%20upon%20how%20culturally%20refined%20he%20is.%20Seen%20through%20a%20comical%20lens%2C%20it%20does%20disservice%20to%20Roy%20Chowdhury%E2%80%99s%20otherwise%20superbly%20calibrated%20performance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20underneath%20all%20this%20fluff%20and%20humour%20also%20lies%20some%20pointed%20(and%20some%20patronising)%20social%20commentary.%20Johar%20touches%20upon%20the%20casual%20sexism%20in%20the%20Randhawa%20family%2C%20even%20with%20the%20women%20singing%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpLyDTEw3Z4%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKaanto%20se%20kheech%20ke%20yeh%20aanchal%2C%20tod%20ke%20bandhan%2C%20baandhi%20payal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20in%20front%20of%20their%20oppressors.%20When%20has%20Johar%20ever%20been%20known%20for%20half-measures%3F%20Rocky%20is%20reformed%20from%20his%20toxic%20masculinity%20by%20embracing%20kathak%20because%20of%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20and%20the%20Chatterjees%20are%20called%20out%20for%20their%20snootiness%20and%20superiority%20complex%20later%20in%20the%20film.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20most%20of%20the%20progressive%20posturing%20%E2%80%93%20possibly%20inspired%20by%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%E2%80%99s%20genre%20of%20films%20%E2%80%94%20is%20delivered%20well%2C%20there%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20painful%20detours.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Churni%20Ganguly%2C%20playing%20Rani%E2%80%99s%20mother%2C%20goes%20on%20a%20lengthy%20tirade%20when%20Rocky%20is%20embarrassed%20to%20go%20lingerie%20shopping%20with%20her.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20scene%20between%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20and%20Alia%20Bhatt%20%E2%80%93%20eerily%20similar%20to%20a%20scene%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ECrazy%20Rich%20Asians%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2018)%20where%20Michelle%20Yeoh%20tells%20Constance%20Wu%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20will%20never%20be%20enough%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20that%20ends%20with%20Bhatt%E2%80%99s%20character%20saying%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekhela%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ehobe%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20game%20is%20on).%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%20the%20oddest%20bit%20of%20appropriation%20from%20Bengal%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKaran%20Johar%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Ki%20Prem%20Kahaani%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20rests%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20its%20two%20excellent%20leads.%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20miss%20a%20beat%20playing%20a%20%E2%80%9890s%20Govinda%E2%80%93meets%E2%80%93Bittu%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBand%20Baaja%20Baraat%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Efool%20%E2%80%93%20is%20able%20to%20turn%20his%20bratty%20character%20into%20someone%20earnest%20in%20the%20blink%20of%20an%20eye.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhatt%2C%20looking%20distressingly%20false%20in%20the%20environs%20of%20a%20newsroom%2C%20and%20while%20holding%20a%20glass%20of%20scotch%20at%20one%20of%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ccultural%E2%80%9D%20evenings%20is%20radiant%20every%20time%20she%E2%80%99s%20around%20Singh.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160231%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-4.00.40.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160231%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-4.00.40.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160231%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-4.00.40-300x127.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160231%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-4.00.40-1024x434.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665641%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22509%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Rocky%20Aur%20Rani%20Kii%20Prem%20Kahaani.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20her%20best%20scenes%20in%20the%20film%20is%20when%20she%E2%80%99s%20thinking%20of%20him%2C%20trying%20to%20douse%20her%20love%20for%20him%20in%20alcohol.%20She%20looks%20at%20her%20colleague%2C%20Soumen%20(Namit%20Das)%20asking%20him%20to%20hug%20her.%20He%E2%80%99s%20a%20little%20taken%20aback%20at%20first%2C%20but%20when%20he%20eventually%20does%20%E2%80%93%20she%20rebuffs%20him.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20tricky%20scene%20where%20Bhatt%20is%20trusted%20to%20navigate%20between%20an%20independent%20woman%20showcasing%20her%20agency%20and%20longing%20for%20someone%20she%20considers%20intellectually%20inferior%2C%20while%20sitting%20beside%20someone%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20fancy%20physically.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJohar%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20ultimately%20a%20fine%20argument%20for%20everyone%20to%20be%20their%20unapologetic%20selves.%20Like%2C%20in%20a%20scene%2C%20Tota%20Roy%20Chowdhury%20performs%20to%20a%20song%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDevdas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(2002)%20at%20a%20Punjabi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esangeet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20ceremony%20%E2%80%93%20inviting%20sniggers%20for%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20audience.%20The%20scene%20gets%20a%20callback%20later%20in%20the%20film%2C%20when%20Roy%20Chowdhury%20and%20Singh%20perform%20a%20revisionist%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDola%20Re%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20appears%20as%20though%20Johar%20has%20finally%20embraced%20his%20reputation%20as%20a%20maker%20of%20fluff%20after%20a%20long%20time%2C%20doubling%20down%20on%20this%20opportunity%20by%20staging%20a%20Durga%20Puja%20of%20Bhansali%20proportions%2C%20a%20funeral%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKabhi%20Khushi%20Kabhie%20Gham%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20proportions%2C%20and%20an%20%E2%80%98intimate%E2%80%99%20wedding%20proposal%20that%20features%20100%20people%20(instead%20of%20500%20background%20dancers%20like%20in%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20songs).%20The%20man%20is%20simply%20incapable%20of%20thinking%20small.%20But%20then%20again%2C%20Johar%20never%20promised%20us%20the%20truth.%20He%20only%20promised%20a%20good%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690541432000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28160424%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-3.58.13.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Frocky-aur-rani-ki-prem-kahaani-karan-johar-ranveer-singh-alia-bhatt-shabana%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20film%20on%20the%20cultural%20gap%20becomes%20an%20occasion%20for%20the%20filmmaker%20to%20subvert%20himself%20without%20losing%20scale%20or%20splendour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Frocky-aur-rani-ki-prem-kahaani-karan-johar-ranveer-singh-alia-bhatt-shabana%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Guns%20%26%20Gulaabs%20to%20drop%20on%20THIS%20date%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690541427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102203355%2Cimgsize-43306.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fguns-gulaabs-trailer-of-rajkummar-rao-dulquer-salmaan-and-adarsh-gauravs-web-show-to-drop-on-this-date%2Farticleshow%2F102203423.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102203423.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20makers%20of%20Guns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs%20starring%20Rajkummar%20Rao%2C%20Dulquer%20Salmaan%2C%20Adarsh%20Gourav%2C%20TJ%20Bhanu%2C%20Gulshan%20Devaiah%2C%20Shreya%20Dhanwanthary%2C%20Pooja%20A%20Gor%20and%20Satish%20Kaushik%20have%20announced%20the%20release%20date%20of%20their%20trailer%2C%20the%20show%20will%20drop%20within%20two%20weeks%20of%20the%20trailer%20launch.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fguns-gulaabs-trailer-of-rajkummar-rao-dulquer-salmaan-an