0the%20chief%20trade%20representative%20at%20the%20New%20Delhi%20office%20of%20the%20Korea%20International%20Trade%20Association%20(KITA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Feconomy%2Fkorean-trade-body-upset-as-plis-stuck-11690482471305.html%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELee%20Young-Ho%2C%20the%20top%20trade%20official%2C%20told%20the%20business%20daily%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20arbitrary%20policy%20changes%20are%20a%20key%20concern%20for%20Korean%20companies%20investing%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20Korean%20trade%20body%20has%20commented%20on%20the%20challenges%20related%20to%20the%20PLI%20scheme%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELee%20further%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20stability%20of%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20worry%20that%20Korean%20companies%20have%20had%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20stability%20of%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20government.%20For%20example%2C%20while%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20was%20very%20open%20in%20attracting%20foreign%20investment%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20production%20process%2C%20there%20have%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20cases%20where%20companies%20have%20not%20received%20their%20incentives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPolicies%20change%20quickly%20and%20easily%2C%20and%20after%20coming%20in%2C%20the%20firms%20have%20not%20received%20the%20incentives%20promised%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Lee.%20This%20could%20hold%20back%20investors%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20noted%20that%20Lee%20did%20not%20cite%20specific%20instances%20on%20this%20matter%2C%20but%20as%20per%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Ftech%2Ftechnology%2Fsamsung-may-lose-pli-sops-for-first-year-on-invoicing-issues%2Farticleshow%2F100712753.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ewithheld%3C%2Fa%3E%20incentives%20claimed%20by%20Samsung%20Electronics%20Co.%20Ltd%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20the%20scheme%20totalling%20Rs%20900%20crore%20on%20the%20sales%20of%20about%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore%2C%20citing%20invoicing%20discrepancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20currently%20in%20advanced%20stage%20of%20discussions%20with%20Government%20of%20India%20on%20the%20incentive%20payout.%20Samsung%20is%20a%20committed%20partner%20of%20India%20for%20over%2026%20years.%20As%20the%20leading%20smartphone%20player%2C%20we%20have%20been%20working%20closely%20with%20various%20stakeholders%20to%20make%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20a%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20Samsung%20spokesperson%20told%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Ffreebies-pli-scheme-manufacturing%5C%22%3EAre%20Government%20Freebies%20Under%20PLI%20Scheme%20Truly%20Necessary%20to%20Enhance%20Manufacturing%20in%20India%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20loopholes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20PLI%20scheme%20is%20one%20of%20the%20initiatives%20under%20the%20flagship%20Atmanirbhar%20Bharat%20Abhiyaan.%20The%20scheme%20is%20aimed%20at%20creating%20more%20jobs%2C%20attracting%20greater%20investments%2C%20reducing%20imports%2C%20and%20making%20India%20a%20global%20manufacturing%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20is%20being%20touted%20as%20the%20panacea%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20manufacturing%20problems%2C%20several%20loopholes%20in%20the%20scheme%20are%20raising%20concerns%20over%20its%20ability%20to%20deliver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20May%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Fcons-products%2Felectronics%2Findia-surpasses-rs-85000-cr-worth-mobile-phone-exports-in-fy23%2Farticleshow%2F99334570.cms%5C%22%3Esurpassed%3C%2Fa%3E%20%2410%20billion%20(Rs%2082%2C000%20crore)%20worth%20smartphone%20exports%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202023%2C%20and%20the%20rise%20in%20exports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fretail.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fconsumer-durables-and-information-technology%2Fmobiles%2Findian-smartphone-export-likely-crossed-over-rs-82000-crore-in-fy-2022-2023%2F99204073%5C%22%3Ewas%20attributed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20PLI%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Raghuram%20Rajan%2C%20former%20governor%20of%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findias-mobile-phone-exports-driven-by-assembly-rather-than-domestic-manufacturing-raghuram-rajan%5C%22%3Eopined%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20boom%20in%20mobile%20phone%20exports%20might%20be%20a%20sign%20of%20concern%20as%20the%20growth%20is%20happening%20on%20the%20back%20of%20assembly%20rather%20than%20genuine%20manufacturing%20within%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20key%20deficiency%20of%20the%20scheme%20is%20that%20the%20subsidy%20is%20paid%20only%20for%20finishing%20the%20phone%20in%20India%2C%20not%20on%20how%20much%20value%20is%20added%20by%20manufacturing%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20matters!%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20very%20little%20apart%20from%20assembly%20is%20done%20in%20India%2C%20though%20manufacturers%20claim%20they%20intend%20to%20do%20more%20in%20future.%20So%20India%20still%20imports%20much%20of%20what%20goes%20into%20the%20mobile%20phone%2C%20and%20when%20we%20correct%20for%20that%2C%20it%20is%20very%20hard%20to%20maintain%20that%20net%20exports%20have%20gone%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20retired%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20professor%20Arun%20Kumar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpli-scheme-subsidies-demand-shortage-jobs%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20despite%20a%20promise%20of%20increased%20profits%2C%20the%20PLI%20scheme%20has%20not%20gained%20momentum%20due%20to%20shortage%20of%20demand.%20If%20one%20cannot%20sell%20more%2C%20the%20subsidy%20will%20also%20not%20accrue%2C%20he%20wrote%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690537545000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28141558%2Fravi-sharma-HCoHGXiDMpE-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsouth-korean-firms-havent-received-the-promised-incentives-as-part-of-pli-scheme-says-top-official%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20top%20official%20from%20the%20Korea%20International%20Trade%20Association%20has%20said%20that%20arbitrary%20policy%20changes%20by%20the%20government%20are%20a%20key%20concern%20for%20Korean%20companies%20investing%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsouth-korean-firms-havent-received-the-promised-incentives-as-part-of-pli-scheme-says-top-official%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%205%20Years%20in%20Jail%2C%20Vernon%20Gonsalves%20and%20Arun%20Ferreira%20Get%20Bail%20in%20Elgar%20Parishad%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28135451%2FUntitled-design-20-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Over%20five%20years%20after%20rights%20activists%20Vernon%20Gonsalves%20and%C2%A0Arun%20Ferreira%20were%20arrested%20for%20their%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20today%2C%20July%2028%2C%20ordered%20for%20their%20release%20on%20bail.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Aniruddha%20Bose%20and%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20observed%20that%20the%20material%20evidence%20available%20against%20Gonsalves%20and%20Ferreira%20%E2%80%9Cdoes%20not%20justify%20their%20continuous%20detention%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBooked%20under%20the%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%201967%2C%20Gonsalves%20and%20Ferreira%20had%20moved%20the%20apex%20court%20last%20year.%20Their%20bail%20applications%20had%20earlier%20been%20rejected%20by%20the%20special%20NIA%20court%20and%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court.%20Senior%20lawyers%20Rebecca%20John%20and%20R.%20Basant%20had%20highlighted%20the%20inordinate%20delay%20in%20the%20commencement%20of%20trial%20in%20the%20case%20as%20one%20of%20the%20main%20grounds%20in%20the%20bail%20plea.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20court%20today%2C%20while%20granting%20them%20bail%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CConsidering%20the%20fact%20that%20almost%20five%20years%20have%20lapsed%20since%20they%20(Gonsalves%20and%20Ferreira)%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%E2%80%A6%20the%20appellants%20have%20made%20out%20a%20case%20for%20granting%20of%20bail.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20lawyers%20had%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20evidence%20against%20the%20arrested%20accused.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20a%20long%20wait%20for%20Arun%20and%20the%20family.%20We%20are%20happy%20with%20the%20news%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ferreira%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Jennifer%20told%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20controversial%20case%20and%20investigation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%2C%20registered%20by%20the%20Pune%20police%20in%20January%202018%20and%20later%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20National%20Investigating%20Agency%20in%202020%2C%20has%20been%20mired%20in%20controversy%20since%20the%20very%20start.%20While%20the%20state%20had%20initially%20claimed%20that%2016%20persons%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20including%20Gonsalves%20and%20Ferreira%20%E2%80%93%20played%20an%20active%20role%20in%20%E2%80%9Cprovoking%E2%80%9D%20the%20gathered%20crowd%20at%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20with%20their%20speeches%20and%20triggering%20violence%20on%20the%20200th-anniversary%20celebration%20of%20the%20battle%20of%20Bhima%20Koregaon%2C%20they%20were%20later%20accused%20of%20being%20%E2%80%9Curban%20Naxals%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20claims%20of%20their%20alleged%20association%20with%20the%20banned%20CPI%20(Maoist)%20organisation%20is%20based%20on%20purported%20emails%20and%20other%20evidence%20allegedly%20retrieved%20from%20the%20electronic%20devices%20belonging%20to%20the%20accused.%20These%20claims%2C%20however%2C%20have%20been%20challenged%20by%20many%20independent%20forensic%20organisations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20such%20investigation%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Felgar-parishad-case-surveillance-pegasus%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20partner%20news%20organisations%20revealed%20that%20at%20least%20nine%20numbers%20belonged%20to%20eight%20activists%2C%20lawyers%20and%20academics%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20were%20either%20persons%20of%20interest%20or%20forensically%20identified%20as%20having%20been%20targeted%20by%20clients%20of%20the%20NSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pegasus%20spyware.%20A%20Massachusetts-based%20digital%20forensics%20firm%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frona-wilson-pegasus-iphone-arsenal%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EArsenal%20Consulting%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20later%20confirmed%20at%20least%20one%20phone%20%E2%80%93%20belonging%20to%20prisoners%E2%80%99%20rights%20activist%20Rona%20Wilson%20%E2%80%93%20was%20definitely%20infected%20by%20the%20malicious%20spyware.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20those%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Elgar%20Parishad%20case%20are%20Sudhir%20Dhawale%2C%20a%20writer%20and%20Mumbai-based%20Dalit%20rights%20activist%3B%20Mahesh%20Raut%2C%20a%20young%20activist%20from%20Gadchiroli%20who%20worked%20on%20displacement%3B%20Shoma%20Sen%2C%20who%20had%20been%20head%20of%20the%20English%20literature%20department%20at%20Nagpur%20University%3B%20advocates%20Arun%20Ferreira%20and%20Sudha%20Bharadwaj%3B%20writer%20Varavara%20Rao%3B%20activist%20Vernon%20Gonsalves%3B%20prisoners%E2%80%99%20rights%20activist%20Rona%20Wilson%3B%20Surendra%20Gadling%2C%20a%20UAPA%20expert%20and%20lawyer%20from%20Nagpur%3B%20tribal%20rights%20activist%20the%20late%20Father%20Stan%20Swamy%3B%20Delhi%20University%20professor%20Hany%20Babu%2C%20scholar%3B%20academic%20Anand%20Teltumbde%3B%20civil%20liberties%20activist%20Gautam%20Navlakha%3B%20and%20members%20of%20the%20cultural%20group%2C%20Kabir%20Kala%20Manch%3A%20Sagar%20Gorkhe%2C%20Ramesh%20Ghaichor%20and%20Jyoti%20Jagtap.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Flaw%2Felgar-parishad-arrested-activists-status%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETeltumbde%2C%20Bharadwaj%20and%20Rao%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20out%20on%20bail%2C%20but%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fill-treatment-of-stan-swamy-in-jail-should-shake-foundation-of-democracy-fellow-prisoner%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESwamy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20died%20last%20year%20allegedly%20due%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20negligence%20and%20failure%20to%20provide%20him%20with%20adequate%20medical%20care.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20other%20accused%20persons%20%E2%80%93%20Sen%20and%20Jagtap%20%E2%80%93%20have%20also%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20court%20is%20likely%20to%20decide%20on%20their%20application%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20reading%20out%20the%20operative%20part%20of%20the%20order%2C%20the%20judges%20said%20that%20Gonsalves%20and%20Ferreira%20are%20both%20granted%20conditional%20bails.%20Gonsalves%E2%80%99s%20prior%20conv