ian%20ambassador%2C%20Sridharan%20Madhusudhanan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20meeting%2C%20Hikmat%20Hajiyev%20said%20that%20the%20Azerbaijani%20side%20is%20concerned%20about%20deepening%20military%20cooperation%20between%20Armenia%20and%20India%20and%20the%20dissemination%20of%20photos%20and%20videos%20in%20the%20media%20about%20transferring%20Indian-made%20weapon%20systems%20to%20Armenia%20through%20Iran%20in%20recent%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20APA%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAzerbaijan%E2%80%99s%20diplomatic%20confrontation%20with%20India%20comes%20amidst%20the%20flashpoint%20of%20Nagorno-Karabakh%20again%20revving%20up%20to%20a%20crisis.%20On%20July%2025%2C%20Armenia%20said%20that%20it%20will%20send%20a%20convoy%20of%20food%20assistance%20to%20the%20breakaway%20region%20that%20has%20been%20facing%20shortages%20due%20to%20a%20blockade.%20Azerbaijan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rferl.org%2Fa%2Fazerbaijan-blocks-armenian-aid-convoy-%2F32522087.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eblocked%20the%20cavalcade%20and%20termed%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cprovocation%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20as%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERadio%20Free%20Europe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Baku%2C%20the%20senior%20Azeri%20official%20claimed%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20delivery%20of%20lethal%20weapons%20to%20Armenia%20came%20against%20ongoing%20negotiations%20for%20a%20peace%20deal%20between%20the%20two%20Eurasian%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmilitarisation%E2%80%9D%20of%20Armenia%20and%20aggravate%20the%20situation%2C%20Hajiyev%20said%20alleged%20Indian%20weapon%20transfers%20were%20%E2%80%9Cobstacles%20to%20the%20establishment%20of%20sustainable%20peace%20and%20security%20in%20the%20South%20Caucasus%20region%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20incompatible%20both%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20self-proclaimed%20foreign%20policy%20based%20on%20the%20norms%20and%20principles%20of%20international%20law%20as%20well%20as%20the%20historical%20%E2%80%98Bandung%20Principles%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Non-Aligned%20Movement%20that%20India%20is%20party%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Azeri%20official%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20APA.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20news%20report%2C%20the%20Indian%20ambassador%20said%20that%20Azerbaijan%E2%80%99s%20concerns%20will%20be%20communicated%20accordingly%20to%20New%20Delhi.%20Madhusudhanan%20also%20apparently%20said%20that%20it%20was%20important%20to%20conduct%20a%20dialogue%20on%20issues%20of%20concern%20in%20bilateral%20relations%2C%20which%20was%20accepted%20by%20Hajiyev.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20official%20response%20from%20India%20till%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20September%2C%20Indian%20media%20reports%20said%20that%20Armenia%20and%20India%20had%20signed%20a%20major%20defence%20deal%20for%20procurement%20of%20Pinaka%20multi-rocket%20launch%20systems%20and%20their%20ammunition.%20It%20was%20only%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20long%20list%20of%20weapons%20that%20Armenia%20was%20shopping%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orfonline.org%2Fexpert-speak%2Findias-pinaka-export-to-armenia-positions-it-against-pan-turkism%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eanalysis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Delhi-based%20think%20tank%20ORF%2C%20the%20defence%20transfer%20meant%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20overtly%20positioned%20itself%20on%20Armenia%E2%80%99s%20side%20in%20the%20Nagorno-Karabakh%20conflict%2C%20and%20has%20consequently%20opted%20to%20resist%20Azerbaijan%20and%20its%20backers%20including%20Turkey%20and%20Pakistan%20as%20well%20as%20Ankara%E2%80%99s%20expansionist%20pan-