lationships-8862180%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20court%20said%20that%20Indian%20society%20considers%20it%20unethical%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20illegal.%20I%20believe%20if%20this%20is%20unethical%2C%20then%20it%20should%20be%20illegal%2C%20too.%20The%20government%20should%20take%20cognisance%20of%20this%20and%20bring%20a%20law%20so%20that%20this%20subculture%20can%20be%20stopped%20and%20women%20can%20be%20protected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20(NFHS-5)%2C%20nearly%2030%25%20or%20every%201%20in%203%20married%20women%20experienced%20domestic%20or%20sexual%20violence%20and%203.1%25%20pregnant%20women%20suffered%20physical%20violence%20during%20their%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20February%202023%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsc-finds-working-of-domestic-violence-act-dismal-4-7-lakh-cases-pending%2Farticleshow%2F98220736.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ecalled%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20domestic%20violence%20act%20%E2%80%9Cdismal%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20there%20were%204.7%20lakh%20domestic%20violence%20cases%20pending%20across%20801%20districts%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690534239000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28125747%2FScreenshot-2023-07-28-at-12.57.20-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbjp-mp-calls-for-ban-on-live-in-relationships-to-protect-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20according%20to%20NFHS-5%20data%2C%20every%201%20in%203%20married%20women%20experienced%20domestic%20or%20sexual%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbjp-mp-calls-for-ban-on-live-in-relationships-to-protect-women%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%