xt-of-prime-minister-narendra-modi-s-speech-at-inauguration-of-international-exhibition-cum-convention-centre-iecc-complex-at-pragati-maidan-in-new-delhi-572394%5C%22%3Eself-serving%20proclamations%20at%20Pragati%20Maidan%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20July%2026%20will%20have%20no%20difficulty%20in%20concluding%20that%20the%20man%20has%20irreversibly%20slipped%20into%20a%20delusional%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20just%20a%20coincidence%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CModi%20ki%20guarantee%E2%80%9D%20spiel%20that%20India%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20third%20largest%20economy%20in%20my%20third%20term%E2%80%9D%20had%20already%20been%20pre-empted%20a%20week%20earlier%20by%20Gautam%20Adani.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhindenburg-report-targeted-misinformation-allegations-discredited-adani-123071800271_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20controversial%20oligarch%20had%20told%20the%20Adani%20Enterprises%E2%80%99%20AGM%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20July%2018%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20economic%20cycles%20are%20getting%20increasingly%20hard%20to%20forecast%2C%20there%20is%20little%20doubt%20that%20India%20%E2%80%93%20already%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%205th%20largest%20economy%20%E2%80%93%20will%20become%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20third%20largest%20economy%20well%20before%202030.%E2%80%9D%20That%20is%20exactly%20the%20timetable%20the%20prime%20minister%20unveiled%20to%20his%20Pragati%20Maidan%20audience.%20Just%20to%20round%20up%20the%20argument%2C%20the%20Hindenburg-bitten%20tycoon%20had%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20well%20understood%20that%20for%20any%20economy%20to%20implement%20policy%20and%20lay%20the%20foundation%20of%20growth%2C%20a%20stable%20government%20is%20critical.%E2%80%9D%20And%2C%20for%20good%20measure%2C%20he%20declared%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmy%20belief%20in%20the%20growth%20story%20of%20our%20%3Ci%3Ematrabhumi%3C%2Fi%3E%20has%20never%20been%20stronger.%E2%80%9D%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F04192003%2Fstatecraft.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-237577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22233%5C%22%3EIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20say%20whether%20any%20kind%20of%20%3Ci%3Ejugalbandi%3C%2Fi%3E%20was%20at%20work%2C%20yet%20the%20convergence%20between%20the%20July%2018%20argument%20and%20the%20July%2026%20assertion%20leaves%20very%20little%20to%20the%20imagination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20kind%20of%20convergence%20was%20anticipated%20about%2080%20years%20ago%20by%20Walter%20Benjamin%2C%20the%20celebrated%20Jewish%20dissident%20in%20Nazi%20Germany%2C%20when%20he%20talked%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fusers.clas.ufl.edu%2Fburt%2FPROUST2021INCOMPLETENOVEL%2Fwalter-benjamin-selected-writings-volume-2-part-1.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cblack%20market%20of%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20As%20Benjamin%20conceptualised%20it%2C%20this%20black%20market%20was%20characterised%20by%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccorrelation%20of%20money%20and%20power%E2%80%9D%2C%20so%20evident%20in%20the%20Germany%20of%20the%201930s%20when%20all%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20industrialists%20had%20lined%20up%20behind%20the%20brutal%20practitioners%20of%20National%20Socialism.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20century%2C%20the%20phenomenon%20has%20already%20manifested%20itself%20in%20many%20countries%20where%20the%20economy%20is%20controlled%20by%20%E2%80%9Ca%20strong%20man%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20politically%20connected%20oligarchs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20we%20have%20our%20own%2C%20slightly%20refined%2C%20version%20because%20we%20have%20this%20little%20irritant%20called%20constitutional%20democracy%2C%20which%20obliges%20the%20black%20marketeers%20of%20power%20to%20go%20through%20the%20motion%20of%20securing%20public%20support%20for%20their%20%E2%80%98growth%20model%E2%80%99.%20As%20far%20as%20the%20ruling%20clique%20is%20concerned%2C%20elections%20are%20a%20necessary%20nuisance.%20Not%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20his%20cohorts%20are%20daunted%20by%20the%20prospect%20of%20having%20to%20contest%20elections.%20Like%20Lionel%20Messi%20proclaimed%2C%20after%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%20for%20Argentina%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20what%20to%20do%20in%20every%20moment.%20We%20know%20how%20to%20win%20a%20game%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20team%20from%20Gujarat%20too%20knows%20a%20thing%20or%20two%20about%20winning%20mandates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20as%20the%20economy%20becomes%20more%20and%20more%20inequitable%20on%20their%20watch%2C%20the%20new%20rulers%20of%20Naya%20Bharat%20know%20how%20to%20seduce%20the%20%3Ci%3Eplebes%3C%2Fi%3E.%20The%20professional%20phrase-makers%20have%20already%20coined%20the%20lilting%20rhyme%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EPai%2C%20pai%2C%20gharib%20ki%20bhali%3C%2Fi%3E%20(Every%20paisa%20in%20the%20poor%E2%80%99s%20interests).%E2%80%9D%20The%20new%20oligarchs%20of%20Naya%20Bharat%20will%2C%20of%20course%2C%20permit%20themselves%20a%20sardonic%20smile.%20Indeed%2C%20a%20cocksure%20prime%20minister%20has%20already%20declared%20himself%20the%20winner%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInherent%20in%20this%20extravagant%20claim%20is%20a%20warning%20to%20all%20those%20who%20have%20a%20constitutional%20duty%20to%20ensure%20fairness%20in%20the%20system%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20the%20higher%20judiciary%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20%E2%80%93%20not%20to%20take%20their%20mandate%20of%20protecting%20norms%20seriously.%20Instead%2C%20they%20must%20be%20prepared%20to%20overlook%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20brazenness%20because%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20contest%20is%20pre-ordained%2C%20if%20not%20pre-arranged.%20A%20bully%E2%80%99s%20perfect%20boast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boast%20comes%20naturally%20because%20beyond%20the%20desi%20oligarchs%2C%20the%20global%20moneyed%20elite%20sees%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20India%20an%20opportunity%20to%20grab%20a%20piece%20of%20the%20action%20for%20itself.%20Of%20this%20global%20segment%2C%20the%20arms-sellers%20and%20dealers%20are%20the%20most%20visible.%20This%20exotic%20and%20mysterious%20band%20of%20businessmen%20have%20perfected%20their%20tool-kit%20for%20trapping%20third%20world%20leaders%20in%20a%20seductive%20bubble%2C%20enticing%20them%20with%20illusions%20of%20power%20and%20potency.%20After%20his%20recent%20massive%20weapons%20deals%20with%20the%20Americans%20and%20the%20French%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20can%20be%20counted%20upon%20to%20reclaim%20his%20%E2%80%9856-inch%E2%80%99%20status%20by%20asserting%20that%20he%20has%20bolstered%20national%20defence%20as%20never%20before%20and%20has%20unprecedentedly%20strengthened%20the%20capabilities%20of%20our%20valiant%20soldiers%20to%20take%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98enemy%E2%80%99.%20In%20the%20same%20breath%2C%20he%20could%20well%20accuse%20the%20Congress%20(with%20its%20earlier%20UPA%20and%20now%20INDIA%20coalition)%20of%20neglecting%20the%20needs%20of%20our%20forces%20and%20for%20short-changing%20the%20brave%20soldier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20%E2%80%98strongmen%E2%80%99%20need%20to%20remain%20%E2%80%98strong%E2%80%99%20by%20procuring%20%E2%80%98cutting-edge%E2%80%99%20weapons%20systems%2C%20just%20as%20the%20arms%20industry%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%20needs%20to%20sell%20their%20ever-expensive%20war%20toys.%20John%20Bolton%2C%20one%20of%20Donald%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20national%20security%20advisers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.ph%2FlTAA8%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealluded%20to%20the%20phenomenon%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSales%20of%20weapons%20systems%20are%20an%20important%20way%20the%20U.S.%20strengthens%20its%20Asian%20allies%2C%20as%20%5BFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%5D%20Macron%20understands.%20Furious%20at%20losing%20a%20submarine%20deal%20with%20Australia%20to%20the%20U.S.%20and%20Britain%2C%20he%20celebrated%20Bastille%20Day%20with%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20announcing%20beforehand%20some%20%249%20billion%20in%20weapons%20sales.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20perhaps%20now%20easy%20to%20understand%20why%20Modi%20has%20not%20found%20the%20time%20or%20the%20inclination%20to%20visit%20a%20burning%20Manipur.%20All%20this%20time%2C%20he%20was%20soaking%20in%20the%20pomp%20and%20spectacle%20of%20%E2%80%98state%20visits%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20US%20and%20France.%20The%20fabled%20event%20manager%20has%20allowed%20himself%20to%20be%20mesmerised%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98events%E2%80%99%20staged%20by%20other%20managers.%20Mentally%20he%20had%20travelled%20as%20far%20away%20as%20he%20could%20from%20the%20ugliness%20that%20is%20eating%20away%20Manipur%20society%20and%20political%20order.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20inconceivable%20that%20the%20vast%20surveillance%20state%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20moral%20shame%20so%20painfully%20captured%20in%20a%20video.%20If%20he%20had%20been%20told%20about%20the%20video%20or%20the%20incident%2C%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20distracted%3B%20if%20he%20did%20not%20know%20of%20it%2C%20the%20pretorian%20guard%20would%20not%20have%20wanted%20to%20spoil%20his%20mood%20as%20he%20was%20being%20serenaded%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20And%2C%20now%20it%20is%20too%20late%20because%20he%20simply%20cannot%20acknowledge%20that%20his%20trusted%20home%20minister%20had%20made%20a%20mess%20of%20a%20delicate%20corner%20of%20India.%20A%20few%20weeks%20of%20moral%20outrage%20by%20bleeding-heart%20liberals%20pale%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20aura%20of%20a%20colossus%20sure-footedly%20striding%20the%20world%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20politician%20who%20relishes%20confrontation%2C%20Modi%20can%20be%20expected%20to%20talk%20his%20way%20out%20of%20the%20Manipur%20shame%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98national%E2%80%99%20media%20can%20be%20relied%20upon%20to%20reaffirm%20his%20credentials%20as%20the%20master%20of%20narratives.%20But%20in%20his%20delusional%20mode%2C%20Modi%20need%20not%20forget%20that%20the%20final%20narrative%20is%20written%20by%20the%20voter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fhkhare%5C%22%3EHarish%20Khare%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20former%20editor-in-chief%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3EThe%20Tribune%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690531287000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28132720%2FModi-Adani.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-new-black-market-of-power-in-naya-bharat%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20statements%20within%20the%20space%20of%20a%20week%2C%20first%20by%20Gautam%20Adani%20and%20then%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20remind%20us%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98correlation%20of%20money%20and%20power%E2%80%99%20so%20central%20to%20the%20kind%20of%20India%20that%20is%20being%20built.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-new-black-market-of-power-in-naya-bharat%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Singapore%20hangs%20first%20woman%20in%2019%20years%20after%20she%20was%20convicted%20of%20trafficking%2031%20grams%20of%20heroin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690530419000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102196839%2Cimgsize-1047689.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsingapore-hangs-first-woman-in-19-years-after-she-was-convicted-of-trafficking-31-grams-of-heroin%2Farticleshow%2F102196698.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20