D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F165682%2Famazon-india-inclusive-workplace-hearing-disability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eensuring%20inclusivity%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewill%20remain%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tarini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20for%20the%20future%2C%20we%20want%20to%20help%20neurodivergent%20entrepreneurs%20get%20funding%20and%20help%20them%20boost%20their%20ventures.%20This%20will%20not%20only%20uplift%20them%20but%20also%20uplift%20the%20people%20of%20their%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20volunteer%20with%20Tarini%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20her%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnaisubah.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enaisubah.org.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690466088000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FTarini-malhotra-3-1690465096.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325345%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Diana%20Award-recipient%20from%20Delhi%2C%20Tarini%20Malhotra%20(18)%20started%20Nai%20Subah%20Foundation%20when%20she%20was%20just%2016%20to%20help%20people%20with%20neurodiversity%20get%20jobs.%20She%20has%20helped%20over%2050%20people%20secure%20jobs%20and%20raised%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20neurodivergent%20artists%20by%20showcasing%20their%20artwork.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325345%2Fdelhi-tarini-malhotra-started-nai-subah-foundation-ngo-for-neurodivergent-community-get-jobs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Pics%3A%2012%20Rare%20%26%20Stunning%20Shots%20Captured%20By%20Wildlife%20Photographers%20Across%20the%20World%22%2C%22conte