0the%20time%2C%20I%20still%20wonder%20how%20this%20eight-year-old%20found%20the%20courage.%20She%20would%20cry%20and%20want%20to%20give%20up%2C%20but%20then%20pick%20herself%20up%20and%20keep%20going%20while%20singing%20songs.%20She%20even%20taught%20her%20songs%20to%20the%20guides%2C%20which%20they%20sang%20together%20on%20the%20peak!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20both%20innocence%20and%20determination%20in%20her%20voice%2C%20Aadya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20climb%20Mount%20Everest%20next!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUntil%20now%2C%20Aadya%E2%80%99s%20father%20covered%20the%20cost%20of%20her%20gear%2C%20but%20she%20is%20now%20seeking%20sponsors%20for%20her%20upcoming%20expeditions.%20If%20you%20wish%20to%20sponsor%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20them%20at%20harshabennur%40gmail.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690379662000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faadya-bennur-1690377858.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D325197%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20trekked%20to%20Everest%20Base%20Camp%20in%202022%2C%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20eight-year-old%20Aadya%20Bennur%20has%20now%20scaled%20Mount%20Kilimanjaro%20with%20her%20father%20Harsha.%20She%20is%20one%20of%20the%20youngest%20mountaineers%20to%20summit%20the%20peak.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325197%2Fbengaluru-aadya-bennur-young-mountaineer-ebc-trek-mt-kilimanjaro-peak-father-shares-routine%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Planning%20a%20Vacation%20With%20Your%20Baby%3F%202%20Friends%20Are%20Taking%20Moms%20%26%20Kids%20to%20Trips%20Across%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMotherhood%20is%20a%20fulfilling%20yet%20challenging%20journey%20that%20often%20brings%20doubts%20to%20our%20minds.%20%E2%80%98Will%20we%20be%20able%20to%20continue%20doing%20the%20things%20we%20love%20as%20we%20did%20before%3F%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20common%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20new%20mother%2C%20I%20know%20I%20have%20these%20doubts.%20And%20I%20felt%20most%20comforted%20when%20I%20spoke%20to%20other%20mothers%20who%20shared%20similar%20experiences.%20If%20a%20simple%20coffee%20with%20a%20friend%20going%20through%20the%20same%20phase%20felt%20relaxing%2C%20imagine%20how%20wonderful%20it%20would%20be%20to%20go%20on%20a%20trip%20together%2C%20just%20mothers%20and%20their%20kids!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThinking%20about%20it%20brings%20a%20smile%20to%20my%20face%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323084%2Fmumbai-mother-son-duo-start-aazol-maharastrian-traditional-snacks-help-rural-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20mothers%3C%2Fa%3E%20Dr%20Saakshi%20Gulati%20(38)%20and%20Dr%20Nikita%20Mathur%20(34)%2C%20are%20making%20it%20come%20true.%20Dentists%20by%20profession%2C%20both%20are%20avid%20travellers.%20When%20they%20became%20mothers%20four%20and%20a%20half%20years%20ago%2C%20people%20told%20them%3A%20%E2%80%98You%20can%E2%80%99t%20travel%20once%20you%20have%20a%20child%E2%80%99.%20But%20they%20were%20determined%20to%20change%20the%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaakshi%E2%80%99s%20first%20trip%20post-motherhood%20was%20to%20Mahabalipuram%20with%20her%20then%20three-month-old%20daughter.%20They%20enjoyed%20it%20so%20much%20that%20the%20couple%20took%20their%20daughter%20to%20Nainital%20and%20Jim%20Corbett%20National%20Park%20when%20she%20turned%20five%20months%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhereas%2C%20Nikita%2C%20who%20stays%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20took%20her%20older%20son%20to%20Mysuru%20when%20he%20was%20three%20months%20old.%20Her%20younger%20son%2C%20who%20is%20five%20months%20old%2C%20has%20already%20been%20to%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20travel%20blogging%20for%20eight%20years.%20After%20I%20had%20a%20child%2C%20people%20told%20me%20that%20it%20would%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20travel.%20Some%20even%20said%20that%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20travel%20with%20a%20baby.%20I%20knew%20that%20it%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20true.%20After%20the%20initial%20three%20months%2C%20which%20were%20tough%2C%20we%20started%20travelling%20slowly.%20We%20had%20such%20a%20blast%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chennai-based%20Saakshi%2C%20who%20is%20a%20teacher%20at%20a%20dental%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThat%20cherished%20female%20friendship%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-gallery%20wp-block-gallery-1%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201088px)%20100vw%2C%201088px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids3-1690375218.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22travel%20with%20kids%20india%20takes%20mothers%20and%20children%20on%20trips%5C%22%20data-id%3D%5C%22325202%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids3-1690375218.jpg%201088w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids3-1690375218-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids3-1690375218-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids3-1690375218-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids3-1690375218-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325202%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaakshi%20and%20Nikita%20bonded%20over%20their%20love%20for%20travel%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20677px)%20100vw%2C%20677px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids2-1690375219.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22677%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22travel%20with%20kids%20india%20takes%20mothers%20and%20children%20on%20trips%5C%22%20data-id%3D%5C%22325203%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids2-1690375219.jpg%20677w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids2-1690375219-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids2-1690375219-500x666.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids2-1690375219-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids2-1690375219-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325203%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22902%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThey%20visit%20each%20place%20before%20announcing%20a%20trip%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20612px)%20100vw%2C%20612px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids4-1690375220.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22612%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22travel%20with%20kids%20india%20takes%20mothers%20and%20children%20on%20trips%5C%22%20data-id%3D%5C%22325204%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids4-1690375220.jpg%20612w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids4-1690375220-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-with-kids4-1690375220-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ft