he%20parents%2C%20and%20the%20schools.%20Preparing%20the%20schools%20has%20become%20the%20main%20focus%20area%20for%20the%20inclusion%20team.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20commonplace%20in%20India%20for%20school%20managements%20to%20deny%20opportunities%20to%20children%20with%20disabilities%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20understanding%2C%20and%20sometimes%20due%20to%20an%20unwillingness%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20responsibility%E2%80%9D.%20Children%20may%20also%20face%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302809%2Fanoushka-jolly-shark-tank-started-kavach-an-app-for-bullying%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebullying%20and%20discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20these%20institutions%2C%20often%20with%20limited%20intervention%20by%20school%20authorities.%20Then%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20accessible%20and%20safe%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20special%20educators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20on%20a%20process%20where%20we%20contact%20schools%2C%20hold%20workshops%20with%20them%2C%20make%20them%20aware%20of%20different%20disabilities%2C%20establish%20relationships%E2%80%A6then%20we%20try%20to%20mainstream%20our%20children.%20For%20at%20least%20a%20year%20of%20support%2C%20we%20provide%20teachers%20with%20strategies%2C%20and%20work%20preventing%20the%20bullying%20of%20even%20parents%E2%80%A6This%20way%20we%E2%80%99ve%20managed%20to%20mainstream%20nine%20children%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCuXG-KtOEuJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCuXG-KtOEuJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fd