the%20director%20of%20the%20film%20Many%20Nayak%20recalled%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20determined%20to%20make%20a%20film%20in%20the%20Chhattisgarhi%20dialect%20and%20to%20name%20it%3Cem%3E%20Kahi%20Debe%20Sandes%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20had%20a%20theme%20in%20my%20mind%20which%20was%20inspired%20by%20my%20childhood%20experiences.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20made%20Nayak%E2%80%99s%20film%20so%20remarkable%20was%20its%20willingness%20to%20take%20on%20the%20matter%20of%20inter-caste%20marriages%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20is%20still%20discouraged%20and%20frowned%20upon%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20it%20was%20among%20the%20first%20artistic%20pieces%20of%20work%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F168844%2Fias-hero-rajasthan-caste-discrimination-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20open%20conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20topics%20we%20still%20skirt%20around%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20film%20ahead%20of%20its%20time%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20the%20early%201960s%2C%20the%20Indian%20film%20industry%20was%20dominated%20by%20Hindi-language%20movies%2C%20thus%20providing%20little%20to%20no%20opportunity%20for%20regional%20script%20movies.%20This%20spell%20ended%20in%201963%20with%20Kundan%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20Bhojpuri%20film%20%3Cem%3EGanga%20Maiya%20Tohe%20Piyari%20Chadhaibo%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20poignant%20film%20on%20widow%20remarriage.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20young%20film%20enthusiast%20Manu%20Nayak%20was%20so%20influenced%20by%20this%20that%20it%20compelled%20him%20to%20make%20a%20Chhattisgarhi%20film%20on%20a%20subject%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Flawyer-dedicated-two-decades-to-helping-inter-caste-couples-love-freely-live-safely%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E